# Data files
# 
# The data is too large to store in git. Source from:
# 
# - Oxford walk network: Generated by osmnx from OpenStreetMap (see scripts/bench_cityseer.py)
# - Telraam pedestrian counts: Extracted from ~/github/robinlovelace/oxflow/data/counters.csv
# - Leeds benchmark data: ~/github/robinlovelace/criticalissues/centrality-benchmark/
#
# To regenerate:
#   1. source .venv/bin/activate
#   2. osmnx download: scripts/fetch_data.py (or run bench scripts which download automatically)
#   3. Telraam data: python3 scripts/extract_telraam_from_oxflow.py
